data.eml:eml: The first record of the genus Cnemaspis Strauch (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Laos with the description of a new species

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Grismer, Lee (2010): The first record of the genus Cnemaspis Strauch (Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Laos with the description of a new species. Zootaxa 2475: 55-63, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.293981
